# Simple web app with AngularJS + Play + MongoDB
=================================

This is a Simple web app developed using AngularJS + Play + MongoDB as an example on how to integrate these frameworks together.
To start and run this app on your machine you will need an installed and running version of [Typesafe Activator](http://typesafe.com/activator) 

More information on how to install and run activator are found in details on my blog: http://marwa-attia.github.io/codefairy
